Template: r7mdaserver/mda-ssl-cert
Type: string
Default: ./sslcert/certificate.pem
Description: Enter full path:
 Specify the full path to the Wildcard certificate
 If certificate file is not found, a self-signed certificate will be generated.

Template: r7mdaserver/mda-ssl-key
Type: string
Default: ./sslcert/key.pem
Description: Enter full path:
 Specify the full path to keyfile of Wildcard certificate
 If keyfile is not found, a self-signed certificate will be generated.

Template: r7mdaserver/mda-dh-key
Type: string
Default: ./sslcert/dhparam.pem
Description: Enter full path:
 Specify the full path to Diffie–Hellman keyfile:
 If Diffie-Hellman keyfile is not found, a new one will be generated.

Template: r7mdaserver/mda-doveadm-key
Type: password
Description: X-Dovecot-API key for Doveadm HTTP-API:

Template: r7mdaserver/mda-doveadm-tls
Type: string
Default: yes
Description: Enable MDA Doveadm TLS

Template: r7mdaserver/mda-nodename
Type: string
Description: X-Dovecot-API key for Doveadm HTTP-API:

